name: Camisole dress
description: This is a clothes lora I trained, using the chilloutmix model as the base model, using the Adafactor optimizer. The dataset currently used is obtained from online public sources, and the training and regularization sets each contain 53 images of a Camisole dress. The dataset does not contain any portraits of real people.
